Chaos Viewer is a progress-visualization tool. It contains no game ROM, no
extracted game assets, and no copyrighted third-party material. Progress data
is generated locally from a decompilation project's own tooling. All game
trademarks and assets remain the property of their respective owners; this
project is unofficial and not affiliated with or endorsed by them. UI design
inspired by the Mizuchi Decomp Atlas (github.com/macabeus/mizuchi).
